des:
You love Chemistry and you think, you want to know about the chemical element for better understanding if you want just ask Alexa to give detail of element.
Chemical lab skill gives a hands-free chemical element information listening experience.

How do I start?
 When you first open the Chemical lab skill, You have to ask ALEXA chemical name and its property.
Skill gives detail about the element like boiling point, melting point, Atomic mass, Atomic number, element appearance, category, phase, symbol and inventor name.

Things to try:
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to detail of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to boiling point of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to melting point of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to Atomic mass of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to Atomic number of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to appearance of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to category of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to phase of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to symbol of {element_name}
• Alexa, ask Chemical lab to inventor of {element_name}

you can access above things by asking Alexa as:
• tell me atomic mass of {neon}
• give me boiling point of {neon}
• what is atomic number of {neon}
etc.
explore the skill you will be gate more interesting details of the chemical element.

This skill under the development its a 0.0 version give the details of the chemical element. where the next version gives extra information and "chemical reaction".
